Perfect, Sir 🙌 — now that your base setup is working, here’s a short & simple roadmap for building your corporate site:

🚀 Steps to Create (in order)

✅ Layout

Create MainLayout.tsx (Navbar + <Outlet /> + Footer).

Ensures every page has consistent structure.

✅ Routing

Setup router/index.tsx with all pages:

/ Home

/about

/services

/industries

/quality

/enquiry

/contact

✅ Navbar & Footer

Add links in Navbar.tsx → navigate between pages.

Simple footer with copyright.

📄 Pages (Skeletons first)

Create all pages in pages/ folder with headings + placeholder text.

Test navigation works.

🎨 Styling

Use TailwindCSS to polish:

Navbar sticky + responsive

Sections with padding and typography

Brand colors

✨ Animations

Add Framer Motion for fade/slide transitions.

📷 Assets & Content

Add company images, product photos, client logos in assets/.

Fill in real content.

🔍 SEO & Build

Add <title> + meta tags in index.html.

Optimize images.

Run npm run build && npm run preview.

📌 Recommended Order:

Layout → Router → Navbar/Footer → Page Skeletons → Styling → Animations → Content → SEO.




